    "Some studies, such as (El Ballouli et al. 2017; Hassan et al. 2018), propose a hybrid approach, combining both source and content features for a more comprehensive analysis.",
    "Lorek et al. (2015) automated the matching between the contents of external links and text content as an evidence feature for classifying tweets as credible or incredible.",
    "Zubiaga et al. (2017) introduced a misinformation detection system to help users identify fake tweets using the conditional random fields algorithm."
